description: By utilizing this tool, you can better understand how much exercise is required to burn off the calories you may be thinking of eating. By lowering the bar and making it easier to comprehend workout time, healthier eating decisions are only a question away.
exampleInteractions: how long will it will take to burn one hundred calories
how long will it will take to burn one hundred calories by biking
name: CalPal
shortDescription: A tool that helps you convert calories to time exercise.
